name: Traditional House #6A - Bale Lumbung
description: It's a pixel sprite 120x120 upscale to 1200x1200 of traditional house from West Nusa Tenggara, Indonesia. You can see this building in Sade Village, Lombok, West Nusa Tenggara. Actually, Bale Lumbung is a barn and is not used as a place to live (a little trivia, lumbung in Indonesia means barn) . Bale Lumbung is house on stilts. It's consist of 2 floor, where the 2nd floor is the place to keep harvest from rats or rodents.
